==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fumous
<hw>Fum"ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>fumosus</ets>, fr. <ets>fumus</ets> smoke: cf. F.
<ets>fumeux</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Producing smoke;
smoky.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Producing fumes; full of fumes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Garlic, onions, mustard, and such-like fumous things.</q>
<rj><qau>Barough (1625).</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fumy</ent>⟦br⟧
